<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">I<sp/>can<sp/>understand<sp/>the<sp/>urge<sp/>to<sp/>clone<sp/>the<sp/>gameplay.<sp/>When</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">you<sp/>have<sp/>a<sp/>world<sp/>made<sp/>of<sp/>voxels/blocks,<sp/>there<sp/>are<sp/>a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">few<sp/>things<sp/>that<sp/>become<sp/>incredibly<sp/>easy<sp/>to<sp/>do<sp/>that<sp/>would</highlight></codeline>
