<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Minecraft<sp/>is<sp/>at<sp/>a<sp/>sort<sp/>of<sp/>local<sp/>maximum,<sp/>a<sp/>sweet<sp/>spot,<sp/>where</highlight></codeline>
