<codeline><highlight class="normal">people<sp/>to<sp/>come<sp/>up<sp/>with<sp/>some<sp/>distinctive<sp/>looks.<sp/>For<sp/>example,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">the<sp/>art<sp/>style<sp/>of<sp/>Continue?9876543210<sp/>was<sp/>one<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>inspirations</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">for<sp/>trying<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>the<sp/>multitexturing<sp/>capabilities<sp/>flexible.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">I&apos;m<sp/>terrible<sp/>at<sp/>art,<sp/>so<sp/>this<sp/>isn&apos;t<sp/>really<sp/>something<sp/>I<sp/>can</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">come<sp/>up<sp/>with<sp/>myself,<sp/>but<sp/>I<sp/>tried<sp/>to<sp/>put<sp/>in<sp/>flexible</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">technology<sp/>that<sp/>could<sp/>be<sp/>used<sp/>multiple<sp/>ways.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">One<sp/>thing<sp/>I<sp/>did<sp/>intentionally<sp/>was<sp/>try<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>it<sp/>possible<sp/>to</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>nicer<sp/>looking<sp/>ground<sp/>terrain,<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>half-height</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">slopes<sp/>and<sp/>&quot;weird<sp/>slopes&quot;.<sp/>There<sp/>are<sp/>Minecraft<sp/>mods<sp/>with</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">drivable<sp/>cars<sp/>and<sp/>they<sp/>just<sp/>go<sp/>up<sp/>these<sp/>blocky<sp/>slopes<sp/>and,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">like,<sp/>what?<sp/>So<sp/>I<sp/>wanted<sp/>you<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>able<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>smoother</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">terrain,<sp/>either<sp/>just<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>look,<sp/>or<sp/>for<sp/>vehicles<sp/>etc.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Also,<sp/>you<sp/>can<sp/>spatially<sp/>cross-fade<sp/>between<sp/>two<sp/>ground<sp/>textures<sp/>for</highlight></codeline>
