<codeline><highlight class="normal">voxels;<sp/>if<sp/>a<sp/>meter<sp/>is<sp/>2<sp/>voxels<sp/>in<sp/>Mineraft<sp/>and<sp/>4<sp/>voxels<sp/>in</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">your<sp/>game,<sp/>and<sp/>you<sp/>draw<sp/>the<sp/>same<sp/>number<sp/>of<sp/>voxels<sp/>due<sp/>to</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">hardware<sp/>limits,<sp/>then<sp/>your<sp/>game<sp/>has<sp/>half<sp/>the<sp/>view<sp/>distance</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">of<sp/>Minecraft.<sp/>Since<sp/>stb_voxel_render<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>keep</highlight></codeline>
